mments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Fri, 22 Mar 2013 13:16:55 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:10:"Promotions";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:30:"http://www.seedprod.com/?p=426";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:674:"<p>On February 13th I started a contest to give away a free Coming Soon Pro Developer License each week to a random tweet. Here are the winners! Congrats to @nycsfmaven, @nnenne , @juzzfranks, @jgbNeatDesign, @gerarddolan, @charisevl! You have each won a free Coming Soon Pro Developers license. Please dm @seedprod your email and I&#8217;ll create your account. If you already own a copy we&#8217;ll extend your license by 1 year. [&#8230;]</p><p>The post <a href="http://www.seedprod.com/tweet-to-win-coming-soon-pro-winners/">Tweet to Win a Coming Soon Pro Developer License Winners</a> appeared first on <a href="http://www.seedprod.com">SeedProd</a>.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"John Turner";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1025:"<p>On February 13th I started a contest to give away a free <a title="Pricing" href="http://www.seedprod.com/pricing/">Coming Soon Pro Developer License</a> each week to a random tweet. Here are the winners!</p>\n<p>Congrats to @nycsfmaven, @nnenne , @juzzfranks, @jgbNeatDesign, @gerarddolan, @charisevl!</p>\n<p>You have each won a free Coming Soon Pro Developers license. Please dm <a href="http://twitter.com/seedprod" target="_blank">@seedprod</a> your email and I&#8217;ll create your account.</p>\n<p>If you already own a copy we&#8217;ll extend your license by 1 year.</p>\n<p>If you did not win continue to enter. I&#8217;m going to start announcing the winner each Friday via the <a href="http://twitter.com/seedprod" target="_blank">@seedprod</a> twitter account. Be sure to follow!</p>\n<p>The post <a href="http://www.seedprod.com/tweet-to-win-coming-soon-pro-winners/">Tweet to Win a Coming Soon Pro Developer License Winners</a> appeared first on <a href="http://www.seedprod.com">SeedProd</a>.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:66:"http://www.seedprod.com/tweet-to-win-coming-soon-pro-winners/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:30:"Coming Soon Pro 3.9.4 Released";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:55:"http://www.seedprod.com/coming-soon-pro-3-9-4-released/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:64:"http://www.seedprod.com/coming-soon-pro-3-9-4-released/#comments";